-- State Bank of Pakistan Approves Faysal Bank's Purchase of RBS' Local Unit
-- Farhan Sharif
-- 2010-07-27T07:21:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/state-bank-of-pakistan-approves-faysal-bank-s-purchase-of-rbs-local-unit.html

          
          
             Pakistan’s central bank approved
Faysal Bank Ltd.’s purchase of RBS Pakistan Ltd., Syed
Wasimuddin, a spokesman for the State Bank of Pakistan, said by
telephone from Karachi today.  
 Faysal bought a 99.4 percent stake in RBS Pakistan on June
16 for 41 million euros ($50.5 million).  
